  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="KT261-kilavi">iravukkuṟikkaṇ talaimakaṉ ciṟaippuṟamākat tōḻikkuc colluvāḷāyc colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">Uttered as if speaking to the confidante, while HE is
          behind the hedge at the night tryst.</p>
      </div>

      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="KT261">
          <l> paḻamaḻai poḻinteṉap pataṉaḻin turukiya</l>
          <l> citaṭṭukkā yeṇṇiṉ cilpeyaṟ kaṭaināṭ</l>
          <l> cēṟṟunilai muṉaiiya ceṅkaṭ kārā</l>
          <l> ṉaḷḷeṉ yāmat taiyeṉak karaiyu</l>
          <l> mañcuvaru poḻuti ṉāṉu meṉkaṇ</l>
          <l> ṭuñcā vāḻi tōḻi kāvalar</l>
          <l> kaṇakkāy vakaiyiṉ varuntiyeṉ</l>
          <l> ṉeñcupuṇ ṇuṟṟa viḻumat tāṉē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg xml:lang="en">
          <l rend="indent2">In the distress from the wound in my heart,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">troubled because of the special manner of [time] calculation</l>
          <l>of the [night] watchmen, my eyes don't sleep, oh friend,</l>
          <l rend="indent">even at the time when fear comes,</l>
          <l rend="indent">when at deepest midnight the red-eyed buffalo cow,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">to whom standing in the mud is disgusting, roars “ai”,</l>
          <l rend="indent3">on the last days of the little rain, when she considers the hollow,</l>
          <l rend="indent4">unripe fruit, which have become soft and rotting,</l>
          <l rend="indent5">because rain has fallen on the fruit.</l>

          <lg type="alternate" sameAs="1+2b" resp="#TVG">
            <l>on the last days of the little rain on the Eḷ corn without grains,</l>
            <l>which have become soft [and] rotting because the old rains have</l>
            <l>drenched it.</l>
          </lg>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
